      <hedline>
        <hl1>Armonk Company Building New Studio</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Peter Beller</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Beller, Peter</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Cine Magnetics of Armonk, NY, which copies videocassettes to DVD and creates videos for airlines, is building $250,000 studio for creating DVD's (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Cine Magnetics, an Armonk company that copies videocassettes to DVD and creates videos for airlines, is spending $250,000 to build a studio for creating DVD's. The company already has three specialized studios. The new studio will handle projects requiring high-quality sound reproduction. It will also be used to create movies that airlines make available to passengers on personal screens.</p>
        <p>Peter Beller</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
